 default/data/ui/views/dragos_indicators.xml
 Dragos OT Security for Splunk App
 Indicators
=============================================================================

PURPOSE

Displays all threat indicators retrieved from the Dragos Platform.

DATA SOURCE

GET /api/v1/indicators
â†’ sourcetype=dragos:indicators

Top-level fields:
- id
- value
- indicator_type
- category
- comment
- first_seen
- last_seen
- updated_at
- confidence
- kill_chain
